cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on developing a robust and accurate pose estimation framework for Unmanned Ground Vehicles (UGVs) in farming applications. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper mentions the use of visual odometry as one of the motion estimation systems used in the pose graph optimization. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions the use of a Markov Random Field assumption as one of the additional constraints used in the pose graph optimization. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the integration of heterogeneous sensory data and the use of a suitable motion model to mitigate cumulative drift. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper mentions the use of a Digital Elevation Model as one of the additional constraints used in the pose graph optimization.
